  "description": "<p><strong>The Opportunity:</strong></p><ul><li>Our Client, leading postal and logistics provider</li><li>Location: Paya Lebar</li><li>Salary: Up to $3200</li><li>Working hours: 8:30am – 6:00pm</li></ul><h3><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></h3><ul><li>Handle 3-way matching of service reports, delivery orders, and invoices.</li><li>Prepare aging reports, reminder letters, and update budget/accrual tracking.</li><li>Maintain shared folders, track license/insurance expiry, and support logistics</li></ul><h3><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></h3><ul><li>2-3 years of property administrative background</li></ul><h3><strong>Next Step:</strong></h3><ul><li>Simply click on 'Apply here' to drop your resume.</li><li>All shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</li></ul><p><br />Saw Wei Xiang</p><p>Direct Line: 9131 6636</p><p>EA License No: 91C2918</p><p>Personnel Registration Number: R24123075</p>",
